message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with automated spine analysis using deep learning techniques, specifically for localisation and identification of vertebrae. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper also discusses the use of anatomical prior and adversarial training, which are relevant to medical imaging (cs.MED) and neural networks (cs.NEURON).
